creator: Monic.ai
descriptionHtml:
Monic.ai - Your Ultimate Learning Copilot
Create assessments, flashcards, summaries, and study guides in seconds!

HOW DOES IT WORK?
We use the world's best Artificial Intelligence (AI) models to make your learning journey so interactive that it feels like watching Tiktok!

Upload your files, any files:
Easily upload any file to the platform, even text and YouTube video links. Simply drag and drop your files or select them from your device.

Generate diverse resources:
Let our advanced AI technology do the heavy lifting. In just seconds, it will analyze your material and generate a set of customized resources to help you learn more effectively.

Start learning:
Start learning with a library of smart study tools and watch as the information sticks. Spaced repetition. Simulated exams. We got it all.
descriptionShort: Create assessments, flashcards, summaries, and study guides in seconds!
